description: Dessert only truck, that actually makes everything right on truck. Menu includes treats like a cupcake stuffed with ice cream, real fruit smoothies, and ice cream cookie brownie sandwich, and our world famous funnel cake sundaes!We were voted 3rd Best Dessert Truck of the year 2014 (world wide). Best Fried Food (fried Brownie Ball) at the Houston Rodeo. 4 time most creative food winner at the Houston Rodeo.
